# prisma
src/generated/prisma/
# Migrations are gitignored because we use prisma db push in production.
# For production safety, keep a backup of the current schema state at:
#   prisma/schema.prisma (tracked in git)
# To restore locally after fresh clone:
#   1. Set DATABASE_URL in .env
#   2. Run: npx prisma db push
prisma/migrations/

